Package ch.obermuhlner.jhuge.collection

Collection classes that store data in external memory (outside of the Java heap).

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractHugeArrayList<E>
    An abstract base class to simplify implementing a huge List that mimics an ArrayList.
    AbstractHugeHashMap<K,V>
    An abstract base class to simplify implementing a huge Map that mimics a HashMap.
    AbstractHugeHashSet<E>
    An abstract base class to simplify implementing a huge Set that mimics a HashSet.
    HugeArrayList<E>
    A mutable List that stores elements in a MemoryManager.
    HugeArrayList.Builder<E>
    Builds a HugeArrayList.
    HugeHashMap<K,V>
    A Map that stores key/value pairs in a MemoryManager.
    HugeHashMap.Builder<K,V>
    Builds a HugeHashMap.
    HugeHashSet<E>
    A Set that stores elements in a MemoryManager.
    HugeHashSet.Builder<E>
    Builds a HugeHashSet.
    ImmutableHugeArrayList<E>
    An immutable List that stores elements in a MemoryManager.
    ImmutableHugeArrayList.Builder<E>
    Builds a ImmutableHugeArrayList.
    ImmutableHugeHashMap<K,V>
    An immutable Map that stores elements in a MemoryManager.
    ImmutableHugeHashMap.Builder<K,V>
    Builds an ImmutableHugeHashMap.
    ImmutableHugeHashSet<E>
    An immutable Set that stores elements in a MemoryManager.
    ImmutableHugeHashSet.Builder<E>
    Builds an ImmutableHugeHashSet.
